Package: amp.sim
Title: Various functions to aid simulation of pharmacometric models
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Richard", "Hooijmaijers", email = "richardhooijmaijers@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre","cph")))
Description: Tools to transform NONMEM models into R syntax so they can be used for
    simulations using the deSolve, RxODE or mrgsolve package. Additionally, functionality is included to aid simulations performed
    directly in NONMEM and to automatically create shiny apps for simulation models.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports:
